Huanglong Scenic and Historic Interest Area in Songpan County, in southwest China's Sichuan Province, is an outstanding natural area with forests, lakes and mountain scenery. It's also known for its rich biodiversity. Many animals call the area home. Check the video to learn more about the animals living in Huanglong. (The video images are provided by Sun Jiapeng and edited by Liu Haibo) (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)